snippet.description:
#WhereIsPushpa #Pushpa2TheRule #AlluArjun

Where is Pushpa? Pushpa 2 - The Rule - Hindi Glimpse !!!

Pushpa 2 - The Rule - Written and Directed by Sukumar. Produced by Naveen Yerneni and Y. Ravi Shankar of Mythri Movie Makers in association with Sukumar Writings,  the film stars Allu Arjun, Fahadh Faasil, Rashmika Mandanna, Dhanunjay, Rao Ramesh, Suneel, Anasuya Bharadwaj & Ajay Ghosh. The film's music is composed by Devi Sri Prasad, with cinematography and editing were performed by Miroslaw Kuba Brozek and Karthika Srinivas respectively.

snippet.title: UNVEILING MY FIRST SUPERCAR !!
snippet.description:
Welcome to the thrilling journey of my first supercar reveal! It has been a long and exciting road to get to this point, and I am beyond thrilled to share it with all of you.

From the initial concept sketches to the countless hours of testing and refining, every step of this journey has been a labor of love. And now, finally, the moment has arrived to unveil this beauty to the world.

This journey has been a wild ride, but I couldn't be more proud of the final result. So come along with me and let's experience the excitement and awe of the first supercar reveal together!

snippet.title: POORI | King Of Poori Recipe | Wheat Poori Recipe Cooking in Village | Crispy Fluffy Puri Recipe
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we cook a large quantity of wheat poori recipe. We use only wheat flour and cold pressed gingelly oil to make this poori recipe healthy and traditional.

Finally, we enjoy the puri recipe with our favorite mutton curry!

The taste is, Crispy and Yummy!

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3739 - 7 Apr 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3739: Kaash Mujhe Car Mil Jae
--------------------------------------------------------
Babita fantasizes about winning the car in the lottery. She fantasizes about taking a long drive with Iyer and spending quality time together. Jetha, meanwhile, prays to God for the lucky draw. He prays for Babita and wishes her success. When Tapu Sena enters the society with a troop of musical instruments, Bhide writes down his "suvichar." They inform Bhide that these plans have been made to celebrate the winner's victory. Everyone is looking forward to the lottery winner's announcement. Stay tuned to find out who wins the grand prize!

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3739, 7 Apr 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Tere Bin Episode 29 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa BB Cream - 5th April 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally presented by Nisa BB Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

snippet.title: Legacy - Amit Bhadana (Official Music Video) | Bintu Pabra | KP Kundu | The Kidd | Vaksh Vimal |
snippet.description:
This song is the fourth single by Amit Bhadana. After Parichay, Aatmvishvas and Father Saab now i bring you Legacy. Through Legacy I am trying to convey a simple message - If you choose not to be the part of the rat race, stay firm on your resolve and never compromise on your principles you can achieve anything under the sun. This song showcase Three major chunks of My life, one in my village where 5 years of my life were spent, second where i spent 20 years in Delhi and my present life where i am fullfilling all my dreams and taking care of my family .You will get a glimpse of my journey from village to city, days of extreme poverty in a new location and my struggle. With hardwork i overcame every hardship and created a better life for myself and my loved ones. I believe that this is just the beginning. I dream of a much better future and need every bit of your support to make it a reality. With quality content, creativity and vision I want to add value to my viewers lives. In the past 6 years I have learnt alot and taught alot (you know it better) and I wish to keep entertaining everyone for the rest of my life. I want to create a legacy that goes on from genaration to generation Please watch this song and don‚Äôt forget to share it with your family and friends. Legacy. Love.

*About* 
------------

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel. 
              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.

snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku

Tere Bin Episode 31 Teaser - 6th April 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ  #sonypal

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

TuNe Pehli Nazar
Jab Nazar Se Milayi Maza Aa gaya

Barq Si Gir Gayi
Kaam Hee Kar Gayi

Bazm E Rindaan Mein Saagar Khanakne Laga
Maikade Pe Barasne Lagi Mastiyaan
Jab Ghata Gir Ke Chaayi Maza Aa gaya

Be Hijabaana Wo Saamne Aagaye
Aur Jawaani Jawaani Se Takra Gayi
Aankh Unki Laree Yoon Meri Aankh Se
Daikh Kar Ye Laraai Maza Aa gaya

Aankh Mein Thee Hayaa Her Mulaqaat Par
Surkh Aariz Hu'ay Wasl Ki Baat Par
Us Ne Sharma Ke Mere Sawaalat Pe
Aise Gardan Jhukaayi Maza Aa gaya

Shaikh Sahib Ka Imaan Bik He Gaya
Daikh Kar Husn E Saqi Pigal He Gaya
Aaj Se Pehle Ye Kite Maghroor The
Lut Gayi Parsaayi Maza Aagaya

Ay Fana Shukr Hai Aaj Baad E Fana
Us Ne Rakh Le Mere Pyaar Kee Aabro

Chaadar E Gul Charhaayi Maza Aagaya

Jab Nazar Se Milayi Maza Aa gaya‚Ä¶.

snippet.title: Barbie | Teaser Trailer 2
snippet.description:
WELCOME TO BARBIE LAND, did you bring your rollerblades? üåü #BarbieTheMovie only in theaters July 21.

To live in Barbie Land is to be a perfect being in a perfect place. Unless you have a full-on existential crisis. Or you‚Äôre a Ken.

From Oscar-nominated writer/director Greta Gerwig (‚ÄúLittle Women,‚Äù ‚ÄúLady Bird‚Äù) comes ‚ÄúBarbie,‚Äù starring Oscar-nominees Margot Robbie (‚ÄúBombshell,‚Äù ‚ÄúI, Tonya‚Äù) and Ryan Gosling (‚ÄúLa La Land,‚Äù ‚ÄúHalf Nelson‚Äù) as Barbie and Ken, alongside America Ferrera (‚ÄúEnd of Watch,‚Äù the ‚ÄúHow to Train Your Dragon‚Äù films), Kate McKinnon (‚ÄúBombshell,‚Äù ‚ÄúYesterday‚Äù), Michael Cera (‚ÄúScott Pilgrim vs. the World,‚Äù ‚ÄúJuno‚Äù), Ariana Greenblatt (‚ÄúAvengers: Infinity War,‚Äù ‚Äú65‚Äù), Issa Rae (‚ÄúThe Photograph,‚Äù ‚ÄúInsecure‚Äù), Rhea Perlman (‚ÄúI‚Äôll See You in My Dreams,‚Äù ‚ÄúMatilda‚Äù), and Will Ferrell (the ‚ÄúAnchorman‚Äù films, ‚ÄúTalladega Nights‚Äù). The film also stars Ana Cruz Kayne (‚ÄúLittle Women‚Äù), Emma Mackey (‚ÄúEmily,‚Äù ‚ÄúSex Education‚Äù), Hari Nef (‚ÄúAssassination Nation,‚Äù ‚ÄúTransparent‚Äù), Alexandra Shipp (the ‚ÄúX-Men‚Äù films), Kingsley Ben-Adir (‚ÄúOne Night in Miami,‚Äù ‚ÄúPeaky Blinders‚Äù), Simu Liu (‚ÄúShang-Chi and the Legend of the Ten Rings‚Äù), Ncuti Gatwa (‚ÄúSex Education‚Äù), Scott Evans (‚ÄúGrace and Frankie‚Äù), Jamie Demetriou (‚ÄúCruella‚Äù), Connor Swindells (‚ÄúSex Education,‚Äù ‚ÄúEmma.‚Äù), Sharon Rooney (‚ÄúDumbo,‚Äù ‚ÄúJerk‚Äù), Nicola Coughlan (‚ÄúBridgerton,‚Äù ‚ÄúDerry Girls‚Äù), Ritu Arya (‚ÄúThe Umbrella Academy‚Äù), Grammy Award-winning singer/songwriter Dua Lipa and Oscar-winner Helen Mirren (‚ÄúThe Queen‚Äù).

Gerwig directed ‚ÄúBarbie‚Äù from a screenplay by Gerwig & Oscar nominee Noah Baumbach (‚ÄúMarriage Story,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Squid and the Whale‚Äù), based on Barbie by Mattel. The film‚Äôs producers are Oscar nominee David Heyman (‚ÄúMarriage Story,‚Äù ‚ÄúGravity‚Äù), Robbie, Tom Ackerley and Robbie Brenner, with Michael Sharp, Josey McNamara, Ynon Kreiz, Courtenay Valenti, Toby Emmerich and Cate Adams serving as executive producers.

Gerwig‚Äôs creative team behind the camera included Oscar-nominated director of photography Rodrigo Prieto (‚ÄúThe Irishman,‚Äù ‚ÄúSilence,‚Äù ‚ÄúBrokeback Mountain‚Äù), six-time Oscar-nominated production designer Sarah Greenwood (‚ÄúBeauty and the Beast,‚Äù ‚ÄúAnna Karenina‚Äù), editor Nick Houy (‚ÄúLittle Women,‚Äù ‚ÄúLady Bird‚Äù), Oscar-winning costume designer Jacqueline Durran (‚ÄúLittle Women,‚Äù ‚ÄúAnna Karenina‚Äù), visual effects supervisor Glen Pratt (‚ÄúPaddington 2,‚Äù ‚ÄúBeauty and the Beast‚Äù), music supervisor George Drakoulias (‚ÄúWhite Noise,‚Äù ‚ÄúMarriage Story‚Äù) and Oscar-winning composer Alexandre Desplat (‚ÄúThe Shape of Water,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Grand Budapest Hotel‚Äù).

Warner Bros. Pictures Presents a Heyday Films Production, a LuckyChap Entertainment Production, a Mattel Production, ‚ÄúBarbie.‚Äù The film will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures and released in theaters only nationwide on July 21, 2023 and beginning internationally on July 19, 2023.

snippet.title: Indian officials move UK PM's wife Akshata to front row after surprise appearance at Padma ceremony
snippet.description:
UK PM Rishi Sunak's wife, Akshata Murty, attended the Padma Awards at the Rashtrapati Bhavan on Wednesday evening. The UK first lady attended the event as her mother, author and philanthropist Sudha Murthy, was conferred the Padma Bhushan award by President Droupadi Murmu. Several reports suggested Akshata was initially seen sitting with her family members in the middle rows, but she was quickly moved to the front row according to protocol. She was seen sitting next to External Affairs Minister S. Jaishankar and other dignitaries. Watch this video to know more.

snippet.title: Friend Request - Season 2 Official Trailer | Badri, Anjali, Chote Miyan, Pratish & Mehek | RVCJ
snippet.description:
The moment we've all been waiting for is finally here,
Presenting to you the Official Trailer of our much-awaited series Friend Request, starring Badri Chavan, Anjali Barot, Arun Kushwah (Chote Miyan), Pratish Mehta, Mehek Mehra & Qabeer Singh

In this season of Friend Request, the gang (Vikram, Munni, Dheeraj, Aditi & Juhi) is back with more drama, more laughs, and new friends! But things aren't as easy as they seem, as they face new challenges. With the introduction of Reyansh, their rival, tensions rise as they compete against each other in the college election. But when an unfavourable situation arises for Aditi, things take a turn for the worse, and Reyansh is quick to capitalize on the situation. Can the gang come together to overcome this new challenge, or will their friendship be tested like never before? Find out in season 2 of Friend Request!

You can binge watch Season 1 here:

snippet.description:
Episode 3737: Chaalu Pandey Arrives At Gada Electronics
--------------------------------------------------------
Finally, the Gokuldham residents reach the store and everyone starts purchasing electronic items. Popatlal buys a roti maker and an electric cloth ironing machine but Jetha calculates the amount becomes 4999, which doesn't make Popatlal illegible for the coupon. Later, Jethalal tries to Babita Ji to give a coupon beforehand but she refuses to take it until she purchases anything. Chalu Pandey arrives at the store and questions Jetha for not informing him about this scheme. Did Chalu Pandey come for an inspection? Will Popatlal get the coupon? Stay tuned!

From Warner Bros. Pictures comes the feature film ‚ÄúBlue Beetle,‚Äù marking the DC Super Hero‚Äôs
first time on the big screen. The film, directed by Angel Manuel Soto, stars Xolo Maridue√±a in the title role as well as his alter ego, Jaime Reyes.

Recent college grad Jaime Reyes returns home full of aspirations for his future, only to find that
home is not quite as he left it. As he searches to find his purpose in the world, fate intervenes when Jaime unexpectedly finds himself in possession of an ancient relic of alien biotechnology: the Scarab. When the Scarab suddenly chooses Jaime to be its symbiotic host, he is bestowed with an incredible suit of armor capable of extraordinary and unpredictable powers, forever changing his destiny as he becomes the Super Hero BLUE BEETLE.
Starring alongside Maridue√±a (‚ÄúCobra Kai‚Äù) are Adriana Barraza (‚ÄúRambo: Last Blood,‚Äù ‚ÄúThor‚Äù),
Dam√≠an Alc√°zar (‚ÄúNarcos,‚Äù ‚ÄúNarcos: Mexico‚Äù), Elpidia Carrillo (‚ÄúMayans M.C.,‚Äù the ‚ÄúPredator‚Äù films), Bruna Marquezine (‚ÄúMaldivas,‚Äù ‚ÄúGod Save the King‚Äù), Raoul Max Trujillo (the ‚ÄúSicario‚Äù films, ‚ÄúMayans M.C.‚Äù), with Oscar winner Susan Sarandon (‚ÄúMonarch,‚Äù ‚ÄúDead Man Walking‚Äù), and George Lopez (the ‚ÄúRio and ‚ÄúSmurf‚Äù franchises). The film also stars Belissa Escobedo (‚ÄúAmerican Horror Stories,‚Äù ‚ÄúHocus Pocus 2‚Äù) and Harvey Guill√©n (‚ÄúWhat We Do in the Shadows‚Äù). Soto (‚ÄúCharm City Kings,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Farm‚Äù) directs from a screenplay by Gareth Dunnet-Alcocer (‚ÄúMiss
Bala‚Äù), based on characters from DC. John Rickard and Zev Foreman are producing, with Walter Hamada, Galen Vaisman and Garrett Grant serving as executive producers. The director‚Äôs creative team behind the scenes includes director of photography Pawel Pogorzelski (‚ÄúMidsommar,‚Äù ‚ÄúHereditary‚Äù), production designer John Billington (‚ÄúBad Boys for Life‚Äù), editor
Craig Alpert (‚ÄúDeadpool 2,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Lost City‚Äù), Oscar-nominated costume designer Mayes C. Rubeo (‚ÄúJojo Rabbit,‚Äù the ‚ÄúThor‚Äù films), visual effects supervisor Kelvin McIlwain (‚ÄúThe Suicide Squad,‚Äù ‚ÄúAquaman‚Äù) and composer Bobby Krlic (‚ÄúMidsommar,‚Äù the ‚ÄúSnowpiercer‚Äù series).
A Warner Bros. Pictures Presentation, a Safran Company Production, ‚ÄúBlue Beetle‚Äù soars into
cinemas in India beginning August 18, 2023. It will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures.

snippet.title: Upasana Kamineni Konidela & Ram Charan Celebrate Baby Shower with Close Friends and Family in Dubai
snippet.description:
Upasana Kamineni Konidela, one of India's leading voices for philanthropy and corporate wellness, and her husband, global icon and actor Ram Charan, celebrated their baby shower in Dubai over the weekend. The intimate gathering was attended by close friends and family who flew in from around the world to celebrate the couple.

The star couple looked stunning in their understated yet chic ensembles. The joyous and unforgettable moment was hosted by Upasana's sisters, Anushpala Kamineni and Sindoori Reddy, who are her true support system. Upasana's grandmother stole our hearts with her ultimate elegance.

Upasana shared special memories of the celebrations with her bestie, Ram Charan, on her Instagram. Her inspiring motherhood journey has been a source of strength for many working women who strive to balance their careers and family life. As a role model, she has encouraged women to pursue their passions and dreams while embracing the joys of motherhood. Throughout her pregnancy, Upasana has maintained her unwavering commitment to philanthropy and corporate wellness as the Vice Chairperson of CSR at Apollo Hospitals and Founder of URLife, tirelessly working to create a positive impact in society.

Upasana Kamineni Konidela and Ram Charan have always been an inspiration to many, and their journey into parenthood is highly anticipated. We wish the couple all the love and happiness as they embark on this beautiful journey¬†together.

Eda is a bright, beautiful young woman working part time with her florist Aunt. She dreams of getting her degree and moving to Italy, but her dreams are shattered when the heir to the Bolat Holding Company cancels her scholarship. 

Now only two things keep her going - her love of flowers and her hatred for Serkan Bolat. When Serkan comes to speak at Eda‚Äôs university, Eda protests strongly. A series of events then leaves these two handcuffed together for most of the day when Eda learns that Serkan really is everything she hates: arrogant, self-centred and a complete control freak. 

When the media mistakenly links the two, Serkan plans to use Eda to get his ex-girlfriend back who had left him and got engaged to another man. The unlikely pair come to an agreement. snippet.title: NEW! Ep 3736 - Bapuji & Tapu Visit Gada Electronics! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | ‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï ‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
Monika Bhadoriya as Bawri
